                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                                <li><strong>Microfiber cloths:</strong> Trap dirt and dust more effectively than traditional rags.</li>
                                <li><strong>Robot vacuum:</strong> Let technology handle the floors while you focus on other areas.</li>
                                <li><strong>All-purpose cleaner:</strong> Reduce the number of products you need to switch between.</li>
                            </ul>
    
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Involve the Whole Family</h2>
